Class CorridorBase<T extends R_Node>

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.CorridorBase<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Corridor
public class CorridorBase<T extends R_Node> extends Object implements Iterable<T>
A corridor is a collection of all R_Node objects for one roadway corridor.
Author:
Douglas Lau
